Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.28,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}KOKORO NO TOBIRA TOZASAZU NI TSUYOKU... TSUYOKU...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.28,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}POWERFULLY WITHOUT LOCKING UP THE HEART'S DOOR... POWERFULLY...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A courageous heart and deduction power!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm that leads us to the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:31.84,Top Italic,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs18}The Matsutake is an expensive, delicious, and very rare mushroom found in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Matsutake picking Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful of the bad hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that one truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.30,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}WATASHI GA KANJITEITA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.30,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}MAYBE I WAS GIVING YOU PAIN
