Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:46.91,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(318.401,102.533)}Mushrooms, Bears, and the Detective Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:46.91,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(318.664,358)}(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushrooms, Bears, and the Detective Boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part One!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we're here to pick Matsutake mushrooms,\Ndon't go wild picking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a limit of three per adult and two per child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you're done, the hotel will cook them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, also, pay attention to the metal fences\Nbecause past them is hunting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hunting area?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are bears there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-bears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over on this side, there aren't any, so you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what kind of place are we\Npicking Matsutake mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy at the hotel said that we'd find a lot here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any here! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Genta-kun, weren't you the one that\Nwanted to pick Matsutake mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to go pick apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because Matsutake mushrooms are the kings of fall food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they're also much more rare and expensive than apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apples are the fruits that Adam and Eve ate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and were banished by God from the Garden\Nof Eden because of this prohibited food,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which can analyze good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it more mysterious than the Matsutake mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it analyzes good and evil, Genta-kun\Nneeds to eat a lot more of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the old testament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the fruit is an apple only because of popular belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the weird look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not making a weird face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By her, do you mean Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara-san's words are harsh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she's really pleasant, smart, and mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think she's mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-but, just because, it's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mitsuhiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything mean, but don't choose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll be too difficult to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a Matsutake mushroom, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.37,Top Italic,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs18}This mushroom is only found in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a Tengutake, a poisonous mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't do this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any hints and the Matsutake\Nmushrooms are too hard to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just look at the surroundings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The needles on the pine trees have\Nbecome a yellow-green, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsutake mushrooms grow near the roots of\Nred pine trees to get nutrition from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means the trees will decay and\Nthe needles will change color.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, for the Matsutake to grow well, there\Nhas to be good soil, water, and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that information, if we look carefully here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, we found the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is one big Matsutake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We finally got our first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are lots of red pine trees with yellow-green needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm going to find some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Needles are a yellow-green color, under the red pine tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found the culprit, Matsutake-san, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've found one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Matsutake picking can\Nbe as interesting as a treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did Genta go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably going to the bathroom somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun was chugging down a lot of mineral water earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not good to get lost somewhere in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go back to places we've been already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun climbed over the first fence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mud marks on the fence are new, and\Nthe spacing in between them is narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's proof that a child climbed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, I can see many red pine trees with yellow-green\Nneedles just past this first fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:07:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun's detective badge is being repaired right\Nnow, so we can't use your tracking glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we have no choice but to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys stay here and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're taking the action all for yourself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to look for him too! We're worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-b-but, on the other side there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuburaya-kun and I will pair up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and Yoshida-san pair up, and we'll search separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, if Kojima-kun comes back on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Professor will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this better than you going by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-you have a point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, be careful, Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over two fences, it's hunting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans have often been mistaken to be wild\Nanimals, and are sometimes shot by hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't rare in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come back here in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you guys can't find him, we'll ask the\Nhotel staff to help us search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to start climbing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun, answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap, where could that guy have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the relationship between you and Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, you two often go to a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and talk about things ordinary children don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you only understand each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like you two are in your own world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not as romantic as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came from the other side of the second fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fence is broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went through here to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way, the other side is the hunting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were to get lost after passing through the first fence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be able to tell the difference between\Nthe Matsutake picking area and the hunting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:10:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun, is that you? Well, we were worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A b-b-b-bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he isn't even a year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cute, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But be careful. Its mother may be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunfire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could a hunter have shot this cub's mother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's the hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he thinks we're animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gun wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hunter is trying to shoot us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to silence us because he thinks\Nwe saw him murder someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were all worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get Matsutake for everyone,\Nand I just kept going farther...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well, at least he returned safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you contacted Haibara and Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, I already called them a while back, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, now those guys are lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko's badge is located in the hunting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They should have known not to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's find them as fast as we can before\Nit gets dark and return to the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, it's impossible for me to get through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.60,Top,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.56,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.992,355.333)}Yasaka Kiyoshi (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.56,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.992,476.667)}Hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.68,Top,,0,0,0,,At a place like this with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two children accidentally wandered in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, have you seen a boy and girl around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I found it! Mitsuhiko's detective badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, neither of them are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:12:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is a pretty big footprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they were both eaten by a bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In reality, bears are afraid of people,\Nand don't think of them as food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's that one, though, the situation is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:24.44,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.328,358)}Saika Matasaburou (67)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:24.44,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,479.333)}Hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.53,Top,,0,0,0,,It has a grudge against all humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:27.28,Top,,0,0,0,,Both of them could have become\Nanother meal before hibernation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the single-eyed giant bear, by the name of Jubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rumor of that bear is actually true then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The long trip here was worth it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:48.55,Top,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with that thing and get revenge for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.992,356.667)}Negoru Tomoya (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.328,478)}Hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know if they have been attacked for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's help them find the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know this area better than they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Conan-kun and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, on that side of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're with that hunter we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are they with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's trying to find us, the witnesses of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we go out like this, we will definitely die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll say he mistook us for a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're there, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's another potato chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably something that both of them dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have left it here to tell\Nus which direction they went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we just use Conan's glasses\Nto locate where Haibara's badge is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, her badge is on the desk at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only fixed your badge because I was\Ntesting some different functions out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was working on it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the place where we\Nfound Mitsuhiko's badge earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by the metal fence with the hole in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then call the people in the hotel, explain the situation\Nto them, and tell them to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They left traces that they were here, but even after\Nlooking for so long we still can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aren't they just running from the bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:16:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there was blood near the place where\Nwe found Mitsuhiko's badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was a new bullet mark\Non the tree next to the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they aren't actually running from a bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko-kun and Haibara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rabbit-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you even think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if that was one of the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My eyes can tell the difference\Nbetween an animal and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the legendary Jubei appears,\Nyou don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do a clean shot and get him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To him this is just like a toy gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to keep your life when\Nyou meet Jubei, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thing can smell humans from far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and will attack anyone without hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A monster that is 2 meters tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one that can kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,20 years ago, I was the person that shot its eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a famous hunter around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear he came from the Southeast and\Nled a mountain running group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after he met Jubei in this mountain,\Nhe decided that he wanted to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mountain running group?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the boss of a hunting group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we can relax if a bear comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Professor, make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ye-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I expected, if that hunter sees\Nus, he'll kill us immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-but, if we shout really loudly, wait until we're\Nnear them and step out in front of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little Yoshida-san is over there with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can take her hostage and kill all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person has already murdered one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the way he fired his gun at us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he came up to this mountain with that other\Nhunter as an excuse to commit his murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you need a license to go hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the body was found in the mountains, wouldn't\Nthey suspect the hunters and their companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, when a license is approved, it stays\Napproved for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once they get a license, they can\Ngo hunting wherever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, there are no restrictions\Nas to who comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the person you kill has a license,\Nthen you will have an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the corpse is found, you could\Nalso say another hunter did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he saw us when we were at the scene of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now his whole plan is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably wants to kill us now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:19:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, instead of leaving these chips so they will\Nfind us, both of us should get out of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking action in an unfamiliar forest is very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, we can only leave this mountain\Nonce we meet up with the Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left the detective badge right by the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa-kun will definitely notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't we talk about it while we're walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we need to figure out some way to contact them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, there's this cub...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who's been following us for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if the hunters meet this cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was done by a giant bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using its claws to take off the outside layer,\Nand then eating the whole inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The distance of the marks is wide, and the position is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was something very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe she gave birth to a cub this winter, so\Nthey should be happily together somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gave birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Jubei a male?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The legend states that the mountain god was\Nalways jealous of the mountain goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People tried to avoid the jealousy of\Nthe mountain god while hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So her name was changed to a male name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.83,Top Italic,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs18}Yagyuu Jubei is a famous samurai from the Feudal Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was changed to be like the swordsman, Yagyuu Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A female bear that's over two meters tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes me even more eager to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just said the exact same thing as my friend did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did that friend of yours happen\Nto come with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because earlier, when you took your camera\Nout of your pocket, I saw pellets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were the kind that fire 9 bullets at once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But earlier you only fired one bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that hunters usually don't carry\Ntwo different types of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My friend forgot to take spare bullets\Nwith him to this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought if I met him on the mountain,\NI'd pass them on to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But will he be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your friend is still alone on this mountain somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been up this mountain many times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We always split up when we come here to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right, Ayumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We Detective Boys decided to go mushroom\Npicking in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And during it, Genta got lost in the hunting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We split into two groups to search for Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Haibara and Mitsuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...discovered a dead body, and have become\Ntargets for the dangerous hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found Genta, and three hunters decided\Nto help us look for Haibara and Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:58.89,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(317.065,102.533)}Mushrooms, Bears, and the Detective Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:58.89,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(319.068,359.867)}(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushrooms, Bears, and the Detective Boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our last chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have none left, Haibara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were trying to escape, I twisted my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was holding it in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, your foot is swelling and its purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll help you treat it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bear with it a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Treat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but I brought this towel and\Na pair of scissors. It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you use the scissors and cut the towel like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! It became a long bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you need to wrap it around the ankle twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then from the bottom, you have to wrap it around to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you pull it tight here, and repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last thing you need to do is\Ntie the knot, and you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.97,0:24:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, I sprained my ankle while we were\Ncamping before, and Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun showed this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He knows everything. He's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also a great leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not even close to being like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.42,0:24:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is that you know this\Nknowledge and can use it after learning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.47,0:25:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this moment, you're my outstanding rescuer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, n-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.27,0:25:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed by the way you said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.32,0:25:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's dangerous staying here on this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.62,0:25:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go to the forest and think carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.66,0:25:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of a way to contact Conan-kun and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.33,0:25:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.06,0:25:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.23,0:25:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.48,0:25:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, near the place where you said, we discovered a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.61,0:25:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was covered with many branches and leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.61,0:25:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died due to a gunshot to the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.11,0:26:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, there was also the corpse of a cub buried nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.99,0:26:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cub?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.91,0:26:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.95,0:26:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cub corpse was under a big boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.25,0:26:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this mountain is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.25,0:26:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave the search of the children to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.29,0:26:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lot should start heading back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.75,0:26:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.38,0:26:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.55,0:26:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cub!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.68,0:26:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought they found them, but it was only two cubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people in the hotel we're staying\Nat are helping us search!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.11,0:26:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the, you guys scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.32,0:26:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.28,0:26:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After sunset, it'll be difficult to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.95,0:26:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why didn't you tell them what really happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.91,0:26:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think one of those hunters might be the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.12,0:26:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not just "maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.12,0:26:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, without a doubt, one of those three is the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.96,0:26:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.13,0:27:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He plans to kill Haibara and Mitsuhiko,\Nwho witnessed his murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.93,0:27:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why are they helping us look for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.06,0:27:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once both of them run out of places\Nto hide, the hunter will shoot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.44,0:27:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll just say he mistook them for a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you figured out who the culprit is, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.11,0:27:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.16,0:27:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't enough clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.41,0:27:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two will tell us who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.79,0:27:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll tell us in a way only we can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.13,0:27:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.59,0:27:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of mushrooms here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.64,0:27:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.35,0:27:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.77,0:27:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are three mushrooms on a branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.77,0:27:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other four are scattered on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.02,0:27:59.40,Top Italic,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs18}Shiitake is another mushroom native to East Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.02,0:27:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the branch, from top to bottom, are\NTengutake, Matsutake, and Shiitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.69,0:28:04.28,Top Italic,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs18}Shimeiji and Hatsutake are also only native to East Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.69,0:28:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the ground are three Shimeiji and one Hatsutake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.61,0:28:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do those mushrooms mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.41,0:28:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.04,0:28:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.33,0:28:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, will they be able to figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.25,0:28:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.38,0:28:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really interested in this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.63,0:28:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the secret code that we worked hard to think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.56,0:28:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.60,0:28:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like we don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.85,0:28:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those guys just really like to pick mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.86,0:28:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's keep going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.61,0:28:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.95,0:28:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought there was a meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.20,0:28:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Professor, stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.54,0:28:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.33,0:28:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one looking for Haibara and Mitsuhiko,\Nthe identity of the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.29,0:28:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.84,0:29:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.92,0:29:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to fall asleep now, because\Nof this tranquilizer dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.76,0:29:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.22,0:29:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh, you're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.26,0:29:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was aiming at the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.35,0:29:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.52,0:29:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the murderer is one of those three!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.86,0:29:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though Haibara and Mitsuhiko were dropping potato chips\Neverywhere, in order to show which way they went,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.82,0:29:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we never actually met up with them, and it\Nseems like they're still trying to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.87,0:29:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also, that hunter's corpse the police\Nfound near the cub's corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.63,0:29:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cub's corpse...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.46,0:29:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's Conan-kun doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.30,0:29:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stun-gun wrist watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he has already figured\Nout our secret mushroom code.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.68,0:29:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.51,0:29:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, after he hits the culprit, we should take\Nthis cub and meet up with the Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.35,0:29:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.78,0:30:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.41,0:30:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.42,0:30:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.84,0:30:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't we stop playing tag, Mr. Murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.34,0:30:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.55,0:30:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.14,0:30:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can already tell, from the mushrooms, who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those seven mushrooms represent the seven of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.11,0:30:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scattered Shimeiji represent us three children.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hatsutake is the Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.61,0:30:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, the ones on the branch are Tengutake,\NMatsutake, and Shiitake,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.41,0:30:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which represent the three hunters and the\Nway they carry their guns on their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.46,0:31:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.54,0:31:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the mushrooms on the branch, only\Nthe Tengutake is a poisonous mushroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.13,0:31:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the culprit is the person who\Nwears his gun on his right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.26,0:31:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-that's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.68,0:31:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.22,0:31:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Tengutake is a poisonous mushroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.14,0:31:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and anyone familiar with ths mountain would know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.85,0:31:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the culprit found it before anyone else,\Nwouldn't he just destroy it right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.15,0:31:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, didn't I say it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.28,0:31:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were looking for mushrooms,﻿\Nand pretended they were culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.36,0:31:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, we found the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.58,0:31:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Matsutake-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.58,0:31:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.04,0:31:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only we would know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.67,0:31:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.50,0:31:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the culprit the code hints at...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.42,0:31:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.35,0:31:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.01,0:32:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the culprit the code hints at is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.89,0:32:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saika Matasaburou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.40,0:32:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.78,0:32:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police have already found the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.24,0:32:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we don't have proof, the murdered\Nvictim was probably, skinny Uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.58,0:32:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your friend who came with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.87,0:32:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were committing your murder, Haibara and\NMitsuhiko came by coincidence, and found the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.25,0:32:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saika-san fired his gun at both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.26,0:32:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, Haibara thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.43,0:32:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If this goes on, he'll definitely end up killing us."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.31,0:32:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.39,0:32:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.64,0:32:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opposition has a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.39,0:32:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-hurry up and use your stun-gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.90,0:32:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's aiming at something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.69,0:32:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-hey, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.61,0:32:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this man was never going to kill Haibara and Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.70,0:33:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real reason this man fired his gun was...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.79,0:33:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.71,0:33:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.01,0:33:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.59,0:33:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.88,0:33:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.88,0:33:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you try to run away, the bear will\Ninstinctively think you're the prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:34:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stare at her, and slowly back away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.64,0:34:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jubei! Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.72,0:34:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, calm your anger and return to the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.69,0:34:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to prepare food for the winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you don't hurry and go, all the hibernation\Nplaces will be taken by other bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.53,0:34:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jubei, you need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.16,0:34:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.62,0:34:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, the cub! Let the cub go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.29,0:34:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That cub is probably Jubei's son! If he's near you, let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.38,0:34:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.27,0:34:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.82,0:35:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saika-san fired his gun to save\NHaibara, Mitsuhiko, and Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.99,0:35:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murdered hunter probably wanted to kill Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.96,0:35:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, trying to stop him, Saika-san shot the hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.21,0:35:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, Haibara and Mitsuhiko came.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.38,0:35:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before Jubei noticed both of them, he fired his gun\Nat them, in order to make them leave the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.56,0:35:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the tree beside the place where we found Mitsuhiko's\Nbadge there were bullet marks, probably made at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.98,0:35:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't he just shout to warn them?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.32,0:35:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you may have noticed earlier, but\Nbears are actually very intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.66,0:35:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had yelled at them, it would have seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.66,0:35:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he fires his gun at them, both sides would get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.25,0:35:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Saika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.38,0:35:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.21,0:36:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we come here to hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.84,0:36:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with trying to kill a bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.72,0:36:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's also the ferocious beast this\Nold man always talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.77,0:36:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one that wounded that bear's eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.94,0:36:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.15,0:36:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.73,0:36:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jubei losing an eye was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.99,0:36:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She exchanged one of her eyes to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.33,0:36:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-exchanged?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.95,0:36:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That happened 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.58,0:36:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the spring season bear hunt, I came up this\Nmountain while it was still covered in snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.31,0:37:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had slipped while walking around the area, and\Nfell down 10 meters, breaking both of my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under the state of my injury, I couldn't even speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.99,0:37:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was when she appeared in front of my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.42,0:37:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew she was going to eat me,\Nso I closed my eyes waiting to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.92,0:37:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead, I felt something warm touch my cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.68,0:37:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was panicking, but when I opened my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.85,0:37:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was licking all of my wounds non-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.77,0:37:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After she finished licking me, she slept next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.99,0:37:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd eat me when she woke up, but instead\Nshe used her black fur to cover me from the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.66,0:37:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could tell that she was really kind-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.79,0:38:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She eventually made me forget the pain in my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.63,0:38:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I heard the sound of gunfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.05,0:38:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had lost one of her eyes, and left my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.48,0:38:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The group of hunters had followed her footsteps,\Nand thought she was trying to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.99,0:38:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means if it wasn't for Jubei, they would never\Nhave found me, and I would have frozen to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.54,0:38:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I went up the mountain everyday, found Jubei,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.08,0:38:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made her go up the mountain\Nwhere no one would find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.22,0:38:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be that the legend of Jubei you told us was...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.39,0:38:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.26,0:38:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a fake story I made up so that people\Nwould become afraid of Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.89,0:39:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But recently, it seems to have had the opposite effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.57,0:39:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hunter is an animal lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.40,0:39:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for the murdered hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.86,0:39:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was hunting the bear, who was the enemy, but was\Nattacked by the hunter, who was supposed to be his ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.70,0:39:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bears are talented animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.75,0:39:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think that the bears are enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.38,0:39:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only if they are unlucky, they will\Nbe seen and attacked by hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.71,0:39:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to stop that rash hunter. That man\Nwanted to hurt Jubei for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.26,0:39:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.52,0:39:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a cheap trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hunter probably used a cheap trick with the cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.07,0:39:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.57,0:39:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as the boy says.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.36,0:39:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man wanted to kill Jubei so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.66,0:39:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he killed one of Jubei's children!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.62,0:40:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hung the corpse on a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.21,0:40:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way that I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.67,0:40:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,murdering a cub just to make its mother come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.93,0:40:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that man was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.47,0:40:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only beast that was ever here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.27,0:40:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One hour later, we met up with the police\Nthat were investigating on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.44,0:40:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old hunter was then taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.61,0:40:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked back at Jubei's mountain, with sad, lonely eyes...
