Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.23,0:41:58.03,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}BUT I WANT TO KEEP ON LIVING WITH YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.15,0:42:03.33,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}TOMADOINAGARA DEMO II TSUNAIDA TE WO HANASANAIDE NE
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.15,0:42:03.33,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}HESITATING IS OKAY, BUT DON'T LET GO OF MY HAND
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.62,0:42:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, the cub's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.50,0:42:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how you knew it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.84,0:42:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.84,0:42:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought Saika-san was trying\Nto track down Jubei and get rid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.30,0:42:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought he would bury the\Ncub and make a tombstone for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.06,0:42:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even knew that Jubei had given birth to cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.06,0:42:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had many chances to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.06,0:42:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why didn't you hurry up and tell us earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.69,0:42:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I did, then Saika-san would have\Nbeen arrested by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.99,0:42:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Jubei would definitely have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.24,0:42:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, how did you figure out that\NAi-kun was hiding with the cub?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.95,0:42:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were cub footprints on a lot of the\Nchips, so I knew they were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.04,0:42:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi-chan would often turn around and look behind us,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.84,0:42:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you knew the bear was following\Nthe cub's footprints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.09,0:43:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bears often have two cubs in one birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.47,0:43:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cub found dead, and the one that was with Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.39,0:43:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My instinct told me that they were her children.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.73,0:43:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jubei was angry because her cub was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.77,0:43:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saika-san wanted to stop Jubei from attacking Haibara\Nand Mitsuhiko, who were with the other cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.28,0:43:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that old man was more worried\Nabout the bear than us humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.83,0:43:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.08,0:43:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can't help that!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.75,0:43:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To that Uncle, Jubei was a friend for 20 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.75,0:43:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.67,0:43:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When an animal lover goes this far, it's rather annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.09,0:43:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, b-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.47,0:43:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.26,0:43:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mother Bear was saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.02,0:43:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope they find a nice place in the forest to hibernate!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.85,0:43:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.41,0:44:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.99,0:44:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.34,0:44:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that boat strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.01,0:44:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.89,0:44:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's capsized!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.31,0:44:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is definitely Tachibana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.94,0:44:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.23,0:44:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Officer, wasn't Tachibana-san wearing a life jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.28,0:44:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I remember he was wearing one this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.70,0:44:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.53,0:44:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why isn't he wearing one?
